      "prompt": "请创建一个完整的 HTML5 游戏。游戏描述：创建一个贪食蛇游戏，规则：\n1. 初始长度3\n2. 可以穿墙\n3. 增加一个AI对手，共同抢食物\n4. 撞击到对手，自己会死亡。 死亡3s后会复活，但长度回归到初始长度\n5. 倒计时2分钟，时间结束时，长度更长的一方获胜。\n                    \n重要技术要求：\n1. 单个 HTML 文件\n2. 使用 Canvas API\n3. Canvas 尺寸必须为 360x640 像素（9:16 竖屏比例）\n4. 在 JavaScript 中设置：canvas.width = 360; canvas.height = 640;\n5. 在 CSS 中设置：canvas { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }\n6. 包含完整游戏循环\n7. 有得分系统\n8. 确保有趣可玩\n\n只返回 HTML 代码，不要其他说明。",
      "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>贪食蛇对战</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n            font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        #gameContainer {\n            position: relative;\n            width: 360px;\n            height: 640px;\n        }\n        #gameCanvas {\n            width: 360px;\n            height: 640px;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            display: block;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);\n        }\n        .overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: white;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n        .hidden {\n            display: none;\n        }\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        .btn {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4fd1c5 0%, #38b2ac 100%);\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 24px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            margin: 10px;\n            transition: transform 0.2s;\n            font-family: inherit;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n        }\n        .score-display {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 20px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            text-align: center;\n            z-index: 5;\n        }\n        .score-value {\n            color: #4fd1c5;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        .timer {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n        .info-text {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            margin: 5px 0;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"gameContainer\">\n        <canvas id=\"gameCanvas\"></canvas>\n        <div id=\"menuOverlay\" class=\"overlay\">\n            <h1>贪食蛇对战</h1>\n            <p class=\"info-text\">控制你的蛇（绿色），与AI蛇（红色）争夺食物。</p>\n            <p class=\"info-text\">规则：初始长度3，可穿墙，撞到对手会死亡，3秒后复活。</p>\n            <p class=\"info-text\">2分钟倒计时结束，长度更长者获胜！</p>\n            <button class=\"btn\" id=\"startBtn\">开始游戏</button>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"gameOverOverlay\" class=\"overlay hidden\">\n            <h1 id=\"resultText\">游戏结束</h1>\n            <p class=\"info-text\" id=\"finalScore\"></p>\n            <button class=\"btn\" id=\"restartBtn\">重新开始</button>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"pauseOverlay\" class=\"overlay hidden\">\n            <h1>游戏暂停</h1>\n            <button class=\"btn\" id=\"resumeBtn\">继续游戏</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"score-display\" id=\"scoreDisplay\">\n            <div>玩家长度: <span class=\"score-value\" id=\"playerScore\">3</span></div>\n            <div>AI长度: <span class=\"score-value\" id=\"aiScore\">3</span></div>\n            <div class=\"timer\">倒计时: <span class=\"score-value\" id=\"timerDisplay\">2:00</span></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // 游戏常量\n        const CANVAS_WIDTH = 360;\n        const CANVAS_HEIGHT = 640;\n        const GRID_SIZE = 20;\n        const COLS = CANVAS_WIDTH / GRID_SIZE;\n        const ROWS = CANVAS_HEIGHT / GRID_SIZE;\n        const INITIAL_LENGTH = 3;\n        const GAME_DURATION = 120; // 2分钟（秒）\n        const RESPAWN_TIME = 3; // 复活时间（秒）\n\n        // 游戏状态\n        let gameState = 'menu'; // menu, playing, paused, gameover\n        let lastTime = 0;\n        let deltaTime = 0;\n        let gameTime = 0;\n        let respawnTimers = { player: 0, ai: 0 };\n\n        // 蛇对象\n        let playerSnake = {\n            body: [],\n            direction: { dx: 1, dy: 0 },\n            nextDirection: { dx: 1, dy: 0 },\n            color: '#4fd1c5', // 青色\n            alive: true,\n            score: INITIAL_LENGTH\n        };\n\n        let aiSnake = {\n            body: [],\n            direction: { dx: -1, dy: 0 },\n            nextDirection: { dx: -1, dy: 0 },\n            color: '#fc8181', // 红色\n            alive: true,\n            score: INITIAL_LENGTH,\n            aiTimer: 0\n        };\n\n        let food = { x: 0, y: 0 };\n\n        // 输入状态\n        const keys = {};\n\n        // Canvas 和上下文\n        const canvas = document.getElementById('gameCanvas');\n        const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n        canvas.width = CANVAS_WIDTH;\n        canvas.height = CANVAS_HEIGHT;\n\n        // DOM 元素\n        const menuOverlay = document.getElementById('menuOverlay');\n        const gameOverOverlay = document.getElementById('gameOverOverlay');\n        const pauseOverlay = document.getElementById('pauseOverlay');\n        const startBtn = document.getElementById('startBtn');\n        const restartBtn = document.getElementById('restartBtn');\n        const resumeBtn = document.getElementById('resumeBtn');\n        const playerScoreEl = document.getElementById('playerScore');\n        const aiScoreEl = document.getElementById('aiScore');\n        const timerDisplayEl = document.getElementById('timerDisplay');\n        const resultText = document.getElementById('resultText');\n        const finalScoreEl = document.getElementById('finalScore');\n\n        // 本地存储最高分\n        let highScore = localStorage.getItem('snakeHighScore') || 0;\n\n        // 初始化游戏\n        function initGame() {\n            // 初始化蛇的位置\n            playerSnake.body = [];\n            for (let i = 0; i < INITIAL_LENGTH; i++) {\n                playerSnake.body.push({ x: 5 - i, y: ROWS - 5 });\n            }\n            playerSnake.direction = { dx: 1, dy: 0 };\n            playerSnake.nextDirection = { dx: 1, dy: 0 };\n            playerSnake.alive = true;\n            playerSnake.score = INITIAL_LENGTH;\n\n            aiSnake.body = [];\n            for (let i = 0; i < INITIAL_LENGTH; i++) {\n                aiSnake.body.push({ x: COLS - 5 + i, y: 5 });\n            }\n            aiSnake.direction = { dx: -1, dy: 0 };\n            aiSnake.nextDirection = { dx: -1, dy: 0 };\n            aiSnake.alive = true;\n            aiSnake.score = INITIAL_LENGTH;\n            aiSnake.aiTimer = 0;\n\n            // 生成食物\n            spawnFood();\n\n            // 重置游戏时间\n            gameTime = GAME_DURATION;\n            respawnTimers.player = 0;\n            respawnTimers.ai = 0;\n\n            // 更新UI\n            updateScoreDisplay();\n        }\n\n        // 生成食物（不与蛇身重叠）\n        function spawnFood() {\n            let valid = false;\n            while (!valid) {\n                food.x = Math.floor(Math.random() * COLS);\n                food.y = Math.floor(Math.random() * ROWS);\n                valid = true;\n                // 检查是否与玩家蛇重叠\n                for (let segment of playerSnake.body) {\n                    if (segment.x === food.x && segment.y === food.y) {\n                        valid = false;\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n                // 检查是否与AI蛇重叠\n                if (valid) {\n                    for (let segment of aiSnake.body) {\n                        if (segment.x === food.x && segment.y === food.y) {\n                            valid = false;\n                            break;\n                        }\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        // 更新游戏逻辑\n        function update(deltaTime) {\n            if (gameState !== 'playing') return;\n\n            // 更新游戏时间\n            gameTime -= deltaTime;\n            if (gameTime <= 0) {\n                gameTime = 0;\n                endGame();\n                return;\n            }\n\n            // 更新复活计时器\n            if (!playerSnake.alive) {\n                respawnTimers.player -= deltaTime;\n                if (respawnTimers.player <= 0) {\n                    respawnSnake('player');\n                }\n            }\n            if (!aiSnake.alive) {\n                respawnTimers.ai -= deltaTime;\n                if (respawnTimers.ai <= 0) {\n                    respawnSnake('ai');\n                }\n            }\n\n            // 更新蛇的移动（每0.15秒移动一次）\n            if (!playerSnake.alive && !aiSnake.alive) return;\n\n            // 处理玩家输入\n            if (playerSnake.alive) {\n                playerSnake.direction = { ...playerSnake.nextDirection };\n            }\n\n            // AI逻辑\n            if (aiSnake.alive) {\n                updateAI(deltaTime);\n                aiSnake.direction = { ...aiSnake.nextDirection };\n            }\n\n            // 移动蛇\n            moveSnake(playerSnake);\n            moveSnake(aiSnake);\n\n            // 碰撞检测\n            checkCollisions();\n\n            // 更新得分显示\n            updateScoreDisplay();\n        }\n\n        // 移动蛇\n        function moveSnake(snake) {\n            if (!snake.alive) return;\n\n            // 计算新头部位置\n            const head = snake.body[0];\n            let newHead = {\n                x: head.x + snake.direction.dx,\n                y: head.y + snake.direction.dy\n            };\n\n            // 穿墙处理\n            if (newHead.x < 0) newHead.x = COLS - 1;\n            if (newHead.x >= COLS) newHead.x = 0;\n            if (newHead.y < 0) newHead.y = ROWS - 1;\n            if (newHead.y >= ROWS) newHead.y = 0;\n\n            // 添加新头部\n            snake.body.unshift(newHead);\n\n            // 检查是否吃到食物\n            if (newHead.x === food.x && newHead.y === food.y) {\n                snake.score++;\n                spawnFood();\n            } else {\n                // 移除尾部\n                snake.body.pop();\n            }\n        }\n\n        // AI行为\n        function updateAI(deltaTime) {\n            aiSnake.aiTimer += deltaTime;\n            if (aiSnake.aiTimer < 0.2) return; // 每0.2秒更新一次方向\n            aiSnake.aiTimer = 0;\n\n            const head = aiSnake.body[0];\n            const possibleDirections = [\n                { dx: 1, dy: 0 },\n                { dx: -1, dy: 0 },\n                { dx: 0, dy: 1 },\n                { dx: 0, dy: -1 }\n            ];\n\n            // 简单AI：朝食物移动，但避免直接撞墙或自身\n            let bestDir = aiSnake.direction;\n            let minDist = Infinity;\n\n            for (let dir of possibleDirections) {\n                // 避免反向移动\n                if (dir.dx === -aiSnake.direction.dx && dir.dy === -aiSnake.direction.dy) continue;\n\n                let newX = head.x + dir.dx;\n                let newY = head.y + dir.dy;\n\n                // 穿墙计算\n                if (newX < 0) newX = COLS - 1;\n                if (newX >= COLS) newX = 0;\n                if (newY < 0) newY = ROWS - 1;\n                if (newY >= ROWS) newY = 0;\n\n                // 检查是否撞到自己（简单检查，不检查整个身体以提高性能）\n                let selfCollision = false;\n                for (let i = 1; i < aiSnake.body.length; i++) {\n                    if (aiSnake.body[i].x === newX && aiSnake.body[i].y === newY) {\n                        selfCollision = true;\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n                if (selfCollision) continue;\n\n                // 计算到食物的距离\n                let dist = Math.abs(newX - food.x) + Math.abs(newY - food.y);\n                if (dist < minDist) {\n                    minDist = dist;\n                    bestDir = dir;\n                }\n            }\n\n            aiSnake.nextDirection = bestDir;\n        }\n\n        // 碰撞检测\n        function checkCollisions() {\n            // 玩家蛇头 vs AI蛇身\n            if (playerSnake.alive && aiSnake.alive) {\n                const playerHead = playerSnake.body[0];\n                for (let i = 0; i < aiSnake.body.length; i++) {\n                    if (playerHead.x === aiSnake.body[i].x && playerHead.y === aiSnake.body[i].y) {\n                        killSnake('player');\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n\n            // AI蛇头 vs 玩家蛇身\n            if (aiSnake.alive && playerSnake.alive) {\n                const aiHead = aiSnake.body[0];\n                for (let i = 0; i < playerSnake.body.length; i++) {\n                    if (aiHead.x === playerSnake.body[i].x && aiHead.y === playerSnake.body[i].y) {\n                        killSnake('ai');\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n\n            // 玩家蛇头 vs 自身（可选，规则未要求，但添加以增加挑战性）\n            if (playerSnake.alive && playerSnake.body.length > 4) {\n                const playerHead = playerSnake.body[0];\n                for (let i = 1; i < playerSnake.body.length; i++) {\n                    if (playerHead.x === playerSnake.body[i].x && playerHead.y === playerSnake.body[i].y) {\n                        killSnake('player');\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n\n            // AI蛇头 vs 自身（可选）\n            if (aiSnake.alive && aiSnake.body.length > 4) {\n                const aiHead = aiSnake.body[0];\n                for (let i = 1; i < aiSnake.body.length; i++) {\n                    if (aiHead.x === aiSnake.body[i].x && aiHead.y === aiSnake.body[i].y) {\n                        killSnake('ai');\n                        break;\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        // 杀死蛇\n        function killSnake(snakeType) {\n            if (snakeType === 'player') {\n                playerSnake.alive = false;\n                respawnTimers.player = RESPAWN_TIME;\n            } else {\n                aiSnake.alive = false;\n                respawnTimers.ai = RESPAWN_TIME;\n            }\n        }\n\n        // 复活蛇\n        function respawnSnake(snakeType) {\n            if (snakeType === 'player') {\n                playerSnake.body = [];\n                for (let i = 0; i < INITIAL_LENGTH; i++) {\n                    playerSnake.body.push({ x: 5 - i, y: ROWS - 5 });\n                }\n                playerSnake.direction = { dx: 1, dy: 0 };\n                playerSnake.nextDirection = { dx: 1, dy: 0 };\n                playerSnake.alive = true;\n                playerSnake.score = INITIAL_LENGTH;\n            } else {\n                aiSnake.body = [];\n                for (let i = 0; i < INITIAL_LENGTH; i++) {\n                    aiSnake.body.push({ x: COLS - 5 + i, y: 5 });\n                }\n                aiSnake.direction = { dx: -1, dy: 0 };\n                aiSnake.nextDirection = { dx: -1, dy: 0 };\n                aiSnake.alive = true;\n                aiSnake.score = INITIAL_LENGTH;\n            }\n        }\n\n        // 渲染游戏\n        function render() {\n            // 清空画布\n            ctx.clearRect(0, 0, CANVAS_WIDTH, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n\n            // 绘制背景网格（可选）\n            ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05)';\n            ctx.lineWidth = 1;\n            for (let x = 0; x <= CANVAS_WIDTH; x += GRID_SIZE) {\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.moveTo(x, 0);\n                ctx.lineTo(x, CANVAS_HEIGHT);\n                ctx.stroke();\n            }\n            for (let y = 0; y <= CANVAS_HEIGHT; y += GRID_SIZE) {\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.moveTo(0, y);\n                ctx.lineTo(CANVAS_WIDTH, y);\n                ctx.stroke();\n            }\n\n            // 绘制食物\n            ctx.fillStyle = '#f6e05e'; // 黄色\n            ctx.beginPath();\n            ctx.arc(\n                food.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                food.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                GRID_SIZE / 2 - 2,\n                0,\n                Math.PI * 2\n            );\n            ctx.fill();\n\n            // 绘制玩家蛇\n            if (playerSnake.alive) {\n                drawSnake(playerSnake);\n            } else {\n                // 显示死亡状态（半透明）\n                ctx.globalAlpha = 0.3;\n                drawSnake(playerSnake);\n                ctx.globalAlpha = 1;\n            }\n\n            // 绘制AI蛇\n            if (aiSnake.alive) {\n                drawSnake(aiSnake);\n            } else {\n                ctx.globalAlpha = 0.3;\n                drawSnake(aiSnake);\n                ctx.globalAlpha = 1;\n            }\n\n            // 绘制复活倒计时（如果死亡）\n            if (!playerSnake.alive) {\n                ctx.fillStyle = 'white';\n                ctx.font = '14px PingFang SC, Microsoft YaHei, sans-serif';\n                ctx.textAlign = 'center';\n                ctx.fillText(\n                    `复活: ${Math.ceil(respawnTimers.player)}s`,\n                    playerSnake.body[0].x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                    playerSnake.body[0].y * GRID_SIZE - 10\n                );\n            }\n            if (!aiSnake.alive) {\n                ctx.fillStyle = 'white';\n                ctx.font = '14px PingFang SC, Microsoft YaHei, sans-serif';\n                ctx.textAlign = 'center';\n                ctx.fillText(\n                    `复活: ${Math.ceil(respawnTimers.ai)}s`,\n                    aiSnake.body[0].x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE / 2,\n                    aiSnake.body[0].y * GRID_SIZE - 10\n                );\n            }\n        }\n\n        // 绘制蛇\n        function drawSnake(snake) {\n            ctx.fillStyle = snake.color;\n            for (let i = 0; i < snake.body.length; i++) {\n                const segment = snake.body[i];\n                const size = i === 0 ? GRID_SIZE - 2 : GRID_SIZE - 4; // 头部稍大\n                const offset = i === 0 ? 1 : 2;\n                ctx.fillRect(\n                    segment.x * GRID_SIZE + offset,\n                    segment.y * GRID_SIZE + offset,\n                    size,\n                    size\n                );\n            }\n\n            // 绘制眼睛（头部）\n            if (snake.body.length > 0) {\n                const head = snake.body[0];\n                ctx.fillStyle = 'white';\n                const eyeSize = 4;\n                const eyeOffset = 5;\n                // 根据方向调整眼睛位置\n                let eyeX1, eyeY1, eyeX2, eyeY2;\n                if (snake.direction.dx === 1) { // 向右\n                    eyeX1 = head.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE - eyeOffset;\n                    eyeY1 = head.y * GRID_SIZE + eyeOffset;\n                    eyeX2 = head.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE - eyeOffset;\n                    eyeY2 = head.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE - eyeOffset;\n                } else if (snake.direction.dx === -1) { // 向左\n                    eyeX1 = head.x * GRID_SIZE + eyeOffset;\n                    eyeY1 = head.y * GRID_SIZE + eyeOffset;\n                    eyeX2 = head.x * GRID_SIZE + eyeOffset;\n                    eyeY2 = head.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE - eyeOffset;\n                } else if (snake.direction.dy === 1) { // 向下\n                    eyeX1 = head.x * GRID_SIZE + eyeOffset;\n                    eyeY1 = head.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE - eyeOffset;\n                    eyeX2 = head.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE - eyeOffset;\n                    eyeY2 = head.y * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE - eyeOffset;\n                } else { // 向上\n                    eyeX1 = head.x * GRID_SIZE + eyeOffset;\n                    eyeY1 = head.y * GRID_SIZE + eyeOffset;\n                    eyeX2 = head.x * GRID_SIZE + GRID_SIZE - eyeOffset;\n                    eyeY2 = head.y * GRID_SIZE + eyeOffset;\n                }\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(eyeX1, eyeY1, eyeSize / 2, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fill();\n                ctx.beginPath();\n                ctx.arc(eyeX2, eyeY2, eyeSize / 2, 0, Math.PI * 2);\n                ctx.fill();\n            }\n        }\n\n        // 处理输入\n        function handleInput(key, pressed) {\n            if (!pressed) return;\n\n            if (gameState === 'playing') {\n                // 玩家控制（箭头键或WASD）\n                switch (key) {\n                    case 'ArrowUp':\n                    case 'w':\n                    case 'W':\n                        if (playerSnake.direction.dy !== 1) {\n                            playerSnake.nextDirection = { dx: 0, dy: -1 };\n                        }\n                        break;\n                    case 'ArrowDown':\n                    case 's':\n                    case 'S':\n                        if (playerSnake.direction.dy !== -1) {\n                            playerSnake.nextDirection = { dx: 0, dy: 1 };\n                        }\n                        break;\n                    case 'ArrowLeft':\n                    case 'a':\n                    case 'A':\n                        if (playerSnake.direction.dx !== 1) {\n                            playerSnake.nextDirection = { dx: -1, dy: 0 };\n                        }\n                        break;\n                    case 'ArrowRight':\n                    case 'd':\n                    case 'D':\n                        if (playerSnake.direction.dx !== -1) {\n                            playerSnake.nextDirection = { dx: 1, dy: 0 };\n                        }\n                        break;\n                    case 'Escape':\n                        pauseGame();\n                        break;\n                }\n            } else if (gameState === 'paused' && key